ml&d=jrWVSpMJYTM9%2F%2BTkK0Hr36npKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=8b8178fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hyd.gov.hk/en/tender_notices/contracts/prequalifications_and_tender_notices/2020/HY202012.html</a><br />\n<br />\nTender Reference\t<br />\nContract No. HY/2020/12<br />\n<br />\nProcuring Department\t<br />\nHighways Department<br />\n<br />\nSubject\t<br />\nDemolition of Down Ramp of West Kowloon Corridor at Yen Chow Street, Sham Shui Po and Construction of Walkway Covers in Sha Tin and Southern (Remaining Works) Districts<br />\n<br />\nDescription\t<br />\nThe works mainly comprise: -<br />\ndemolition of an existing 180 meters(m) long down ramp of the West Kowloon Corridor at the junction of Tung Chau Street and Yen Chow Street, Sham Shui Po;<br />\nmodification/reconstruction of existing footpaths, carriageways and other structures to be affected by the works mentioned in (a) above;<br />\nconstruction of a walkway cover of about 485m long at Lok King Street of Sha Tin District;<br />\nconstruction of a walkway cover of about 40m long at Pok Fu Lam Road of Southern District; and<br />\nancillary works including public lighting, drainage, landscaping and environmental mitigation measures, etc.<br />\nThe works are scheduled to commence in June 2021 and will take about 18 months to complete<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRIP &amp; 瑪麗醫院轉車站 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b456229a1781b41b64984932937c272a6457a0","tid":2464320,"uid":312744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"837c6561f66fc3e9a859992fa1bb7c49a67d1945","tid":2464320,"uid":39780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de1a9b1f182eb2c990190f3ea7b523573ef4319a","tid":2464320,"uid":312744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e4e894248d25fe6ced5fc9dc0b53c16f23cb522","tid":2464320,"uid":39780,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T11:11:51.000Z","msg":"hello 我想問下你地會唔會幻想屌巴士個死氣喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonde